BrightBlade, Rage

* BrightBlade slowed to a trot in order to let Gangon catch up to her, there 
was no sense in leaving him behind.

^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

* Rage caught up to Scourge and heard his words, she must not act hostile 
against the other bots of his team.
But she was so hungry and needed to eat, her stomach growled as she 
continued beside him.
Rage looked around and suddenly stopped, it was another big metal thing!
She looked at Scourge and then back at the metal structure, this one looked 
even meaner then the one before!
Rage almost felt as if she was going to be swallowed up by it, it frightened 
her!*
